Application that simulates a pomodoro for the Pomodoro technique. 

Jose Manuel Beas is the author of the java source code for this example.

With this example we'll explore:

- how to integrate ant tasks into rake scripts.
- the use of the JRuby CLASSPATH variable
- how to access to the JRuby runtime variable
- how to import java classes into ruby code
- how to integrate a ruby testing framework, RSpec, into a java project
